<emphasis id="F9A6EAC0991AFFD9CD483AA9FE2DF818" box="[297,476,1942,1965]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">Lithodes paulayi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="E29557BB991AFFD9CD823AAAFDE6F819" box="[483,535,1941,1964]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" rank="species">n.sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, holotype male 113 × 102 mm, Guam. (a) carapace, dorsal. (b) lateral view of anterior carapace and rostrum. (c) dorsal view of right anterolateral carapace and appendages. (d) lateral view of right anterolateral carapace and appendages. (e) right third walking leg, dorsal. Scales = 1 cm.
